text: István Prihoda (15 November 1891 - 22 November 1965) was a Hungarian sports shooter. He competed in three events at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1891 births Category:1965 deaths Category:Sportspeople from Cluj-Napoca Category:Hungarian male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Hungary Category:Shooters at the 1912 Summer Olympics
